<bibRefCitation author="Ballantyne, L. &amp; Menayah, R." box="[815,1177,1574,1598]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" pagination="323 - 328" refId="ref122856" refString="Ballantyne, L. A &amp; Menayah, R. (2000) Redescription of the Synchronous Firefly, Pteroptyx tener Olivier (Coleoptera: Lampyridae), of Kampung Kuantan, Selangor. Malayan Nature Journal, 54 - 4, 323 - 328." type="journal article" year="2000">Ballantyne and Menayah (2000</bibRefCitation>
